        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>
                At STAYFIT, we aim to bring fitness to everyone through personalized workout plans,
                diet guidance, and progress tracking tools.
            </p>

            <h3>Why Choose Us?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Easy-to-follow workout programs</li>
